<h4 id="trail-guide">Trail Guide</h4>

<ul>
  <li><strong>Duration</strong>:
    <ul>
      <li>via abandoned road: 1.0 miles, 1:00 up; 0:30 DOWN.
        <ul>
          <li>In 2020, I took it slow, with no other hills first. It was exhausting.  1:00 includes climbing the tower stairs.</li>
          <li>Allow an extra 5-10 minutes for setup/teardown, betause Iâ€™m timid at heights.</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li>via AT 1.4 miles, 0:45 down</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li><strong>Navigation</strong>: You have two choices.  Both depart to your left, facing the direction you drove in:
    <ul>
      <li>Follow the AT north from the gap road for 1.4 miles to the tower.</li>
      <li>Follow the dirt road north from the gap for about the same. It is a steep climb with no level spots.</li>
      <li>The dirt road is 0.4 shorter.  If you take the trail, watch for the short side trail to your R (to the tower) when you reach the summit.</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li><strong>Trailhead altitude</strong>: about 3897</li>
  <li><strong>Summit altitude</strong>: 4627</li>
  <li><strong>GPS tracks/waypoints</strong>:
    <ul>
      <li>Trailhead: 35.26791,-83.57247</li>
      <li>Summit: 35.2771,-83.5774</li>
      <li>Grid Square: EM85fg</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

